article.description: — Isaiah Stevens scored 24 points as Colorado State beat Northern Colorado 83-64 on Tuesday.
article.headline: Stevens scores 24 as Colorado State tops Northern Colorado 83-64
article.linkText: Stevens scores 24 as Colorado State tops Northern Colorado 83-64
article.story: GREELEY, Colo. -- — Isaiah Stevens scored 24 points as Colorado State beat Northern Colorado 83-64 on Tuesday. Stevens was 8 of 15 shooting, including 4 for 5 from 3-point range, and went 4 for 4 from the line for the Rams (3-0). Joel Scott scored 20 points while going 6 of 10 from the floor, including 1 for 4 from 3-point range, and 7 for 12 from the line, and added six rebounds. Nique Clifford had 11 points and was 4 of 8 shooting (3 for 5 from 3-point range). Dejour Reaves finished with 20 points and six rebounds for the Bears (2-1). Brock Wisne added 15 points for Northern Colorado. Saint Thomas also had 11 points, 15 rebounds and two steals. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
